text: The 1993 Missouri Valley Conference men's soccer season was the 3rd season of men's varsity soccer in the conference. The 1993 Missouri Valley Conference Men's Soccer Tournament was hosted and won by Creighton. == Teams == == MVC Tournament == == See also == * Missouri Valley Conference * Missouri Valley Conference men's soccer tournament * 1993 NCAA Division I men's soccer season * 1993 in American soccer == References == Category:Missouri Valley Conference Category:1993 NCAA Division I men's soccer season
